pageContext.claim: “If you look at that large group, sometimes it gets up to 17,000 people, they say. Today they said it's really gets bigger and bigger. And doesn't make any difference, because they're not coming in. They're not coming in. The military is all ready.”
pageContext.analysis: The caravan was initially estimated at 7,000 but the numbers had dwindled to about 3,000 at the time Trump said it was 17,000.
